<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١١٣٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةَ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6543">أَبُو جَمْرَةَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كَانَ صَلَاةُ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> ثَلَاثَ عَشْرَةَ رَكْعَةً، يَعْنِي بِاللَّيْلِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>